pipeline_summary.name: Procurement Supplier Validation Pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Validates and standardizes supplier data by reconciling names against a known database (Wikidata) for improved data quality in procurement systems. Ingests a CSV of basic supplier information, converts it to JSON, reconciles supplier names, and exports the enriched data to CSV.

components.name: Load and Modify Data
components.description: Ingests the supplier CSV, standardizes formats and converts it to JSON using the loadandmodify service.

components.name: Entity Reconciliation (Wikidata)
components.description: Disambiguates supplier_name values by querying the Wikidata API and adds canonical entity IDs/links.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of load_and_modify_data.

components.name: Save Final Data
components.description: Exports the validated and enriched supplier data to a CSV file using the save service.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of reconcile_supplier_names.
